## <T tKey="storybook.a11y.title">Accessibility</T>

### <T tKey="storybook.a11y.keyboardNavigation">Keyboard Interaction</T>

| <T tKey="storybook.demo.key">Key</T> | <T tKey="storybook.demo.action">Action</T> |
|-----|--------|
| `Tab` | <T tKey="storybook.demo.moveFocus">Move focus to button</T> |
| `Enter` | <T tKey="storybook.demo.activateButton">Activate button</T> |
| `Space` | <T tKey="storybook.demo.activateButton">Activate button</T> |

### <T tKey="storybook.a11y.screenReader">Screen Reader</T>

<T tKey="storybook.demo.screenReaderDescription">Buttons are announced as "button" role. Include descriptive text.</T>

```tsx
// Good - clear action
<Button><T tKey="platform.common.saveChanges">Save Changes</T></Button>

// Avoid - unclear
<Button><T tKey="storybook.demo.clickHere">Click Here</T></Button>
```

### <T tKey="storybook.a11y.focusManagement">Focus</T>

<T tKey="storybook.demo.focusDescription">Focus ring is visible on keyboard focus. Do not remove or hide it.</T>

## <T tKey="storybook.bestPractices.do">Do</T> and <T tKey="storybook.bestPractices.dont">Don't</T>

### <T tKey="storybook.bestPractices.do">Do</T>

- <T tKey="storybook.demo.useActionVerbs">Use action verbs</T> (<T tKey="platform.common.save">Save</T>, <T tKey="platform.common.submit">Submit</T>, <T tKey="platform.common.delete">Delete</T>)
- <T tKey="storybook.demo.keepTextConcise">Keep text concise</T> (2-3 words)
- <T tKey="storybook.demo.usePrimaryForMain">Use Primary for the main action</T>
- <T tKey="storybook.demo.addIconsForClarity">Add icons for visual clarity</T>

### <T tKey="storybook.bestPractices.dont">Don't</T>

- <T tKey="storybook.demo.multiplePrimaryButtons">Use multiple Primary buttons in one section</T>
- <T tKey="storybook.demo.disableWithoutExplanation">Disable without explanation</T>
- <T tKey="storybook.demo.useVagueText">Use vague text like "Click Here"</T>
- <T tKey="storybook.demo.mixButtonStyles">Mix button styles inconsistently</T>

## <T tKey="storybook.demo.dataTestIdConvention">data-testid Convention</T>

```tsx
<Button data-testid="save-button"><T tKey="platform.common.save">Save</T></Button>
<Button data-testid="delete-button"><T tKey="platform.common.delete">Delete</T></Button>
<Button data-testid="cancel-button"><T tKey="platform.common.cancel">Cancel</T></Button>
```

## <T tKey="storybook.demo.migrationNotes">Migration Notes</T>

<T tKey="storybook.demo.migrationDescription">If migrating from custom buttons:</T>

1. <T tKey="storybook.demo.replaceCustomButtons">Replace custom button components with DS `Button`</T>
2. <T tKey="storybook.demo.mapOldVariants">Map old variants to `primary`, `secondary`, `tertiary`</T>
3. <T tKey="storybook.demo.replaceCustomIcons">Replace custom icons with DS icon registry</T>
4. <T tKey="storybook.demo.removeInlineStyles">Remove any inline color styles</T>
